
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-savi-dhcp-34.txt'>
    <title>"SAVI Solution for DHCP", Jun Bi, Jianping Wu, Guang Yao, Fred Baker</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-ietf-savi-dhcp-34.txt</link>
    <description>This document specifies the procedure for creating a binding between a DHCPv4/DHCPv6-assigned IP address and a binding anchor on a Source Address Validation Improvements (SAVI) device.  The bindings set up by this procedure are used to filter packets with forged source IP addresses.  This mechanism complements BCP 38 ingress filtering, providing finer-grained source IP address validation.</description>
    <dc:date>2015-02-19T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
